data.description: Discover your dream home with an exciting new feature – an assumable loan option for qualified veterans! Welcome to 7 Karen Drive, Rising, MD 21911, a stunning Colonial residence in the sought-after Chantilly Manor neighborhood. This home is tailor-made for the discerning second-time or move-up buyer, offering both luxury and convenience.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the fresh, modern updates that have transformed this home into a true gem. The kitchen has been tastefully upgraded with brand-new appliances, including a dishwasher and built-in microwave, offering both style and functionality. It's a perfect space for creating culinary delights or enjoying morning coffee.  The first-floor living room has been adorned with luxurious vinyl plank flooring, providing both durability and elegance. Your living space is now truly a statement of comfort and style.  The master bedroom is a haven of tranquility. It now boasts new vinyl plank flooring, an elegant entry door, and a double granite counter vanity, creating a space of modern sophistication. Fresh paint and walk-in closet flooring upgrades add the finishing touches. The master bathroom features a new toilet, ensuring everything is fresh and up-to-date.  The second floor continues the theme of luxury with vinyl plank flooring throughout the common hallway and three bedrooms. Each bedroom has been thoughtfully painted to create serene retreats. Ceiling fans have been installed in two bedrooms for comfort and style. The hallway bathroom is now adorned with a granite counter vanity and a new toilet.  In the basement, you'll find brand-new carpet and padding, creating a cozy and inviting space for gatherings and relaxation. Additionally, a new water treatment system and radon system have been installed, ensuring the highest quality of life.  The exterior has also seen remarkable improvements. Multiple trees have been removed to create a fresh and inviting landscape, while six-foot perimeter bushes offer a touch of privacy and serenity. The rear awning has been replaced with a SunTuf roof panel, and a paver patio and sidewalks leading to the pool area have been installed, creating an ideal outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. A fence and shed with electricity/outlet provide added convenience.  The swimming pool has a new motor, guaranteeing endless hours of enjoyment and refreshment.  The purchase of this home also includes additional inclusions, such as a Craftsman Riding Lawn Mower, an active 20 Pool Vacuum cleaner, a pool box storage, a pool net skimmer, four poolside chairs and an umbrella, and an Ikea PAX Wardrobe combination for added convenience and luxury.  With all these remarkable upgrades, this home is truly a turnkey opportunity for those looking to elevate their living experience. The limited availability of such a well-appointed home in the Chantilly Manor neighborhood creates a sense of urgency. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home.  This residence offers not just a home, but a lifestyle. With a corner lot of 1.29 acres, this home provides the privacy and space you desire. No HOA means you have the freedom to enjoy your property as you see fit. Additionally, this neighborhood connects to the golf course and clubhouse, making it perfect for golf enthusiasts.  Conveniently located near I-95 and Rt. 40, and just minutes from the town of Rising Sun, this home ensures easy access to daily amenities and commuting routes.  Hesitation is not an option – this rare gem will not stay on the market for long. Embrace the opportunity to experience luxury, comfort, and the perfect lifestyle at 7 Karen Drive. Your dream home awaits!"
